                      className="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-indigo-200 transition-all cursor-pointer flex flex-col"
                    >
                      <div className="relative aspect-video overflow-hidden">
                        <img 
                          src={saved.modifiedImage} 
                          alt={saved.style}
                          className="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110" 
                        />
                        <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-end p-4">
                          <span className="text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full">View Design</span>
                        </div>
                        <button 
                          onClick={(e) => handleDeleteSaved(e, saved.id)}
                          className="absolute top-3 right-3 w-8 h-8 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 hover:bg-red-500 transition-all"
                          title="Delete Design"
                        >
                          <svg className="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" />
                          </svg>
                        </button>
                      </div>
                      <div className="p-4">
                        <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                          <h4 className="font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">{saved.style}</h4>
                          <span className="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-medium">
                            {new Date(saved.timestamp).toLocaleDateString()}
                          </span>
                        </div>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-500">Reimagined Interior</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            )}
          </div>

          {/* Right Column: AI Consultant Chat */}
          <div className="lg:col-span-4">
            <div className="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
              <ChatInterface 
                currentImage={modifiedImage || originalImage} 
                onEditRequested={handleEditRequested}
              />

              <div className="p-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-[2rem] text-white shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative">
                <div className="relative z-10">
                  <div className="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-indigo-400">
                    <svg className="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-2 font-display">Expert Guidance</h4>
                  <p className="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    "Lumina can help you pick matching paint colors, find similar rugs, or even suggest where to place your indoor plants."
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div className="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 w-32 h-32 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  );
};

export default App;

payload.text:
Lumina Space ko React se Flutter mein convert karna kaafi interesting aur straightforward project hai. Chonkay aap core logic (Gemini API calls aur image processing) samajh chukay hain, aap ko sirf UI framework aur language (JavaScript to Dart) change karni hogi.

Yahan aik high-level roadmap hai ke aap isse Flutter mein kaise banayenge:

### 1. Key Dependencies (pubspec.yaml)
Sabse pehle aapko Flutter project mein yeh packages add karne honge:
*   `google_generative_ai`: Gemini API use karne ke liye.
*   `image_picker`: Camera se photo lene ya gallery se upload karne ke liye.
*   `flutter_riverpod` ya `provider`: State management ke liye.
*   `http`: API results download karne ke liye.
*   `before_after`: Compare slider feature ke liye.

### 2. Logic Translation (Services)
Aapka `geminiService.ts` ab aik Dart class ban jayega. 

```dart
// services/gemini_service.dart
import 'package:google_generative_ai/google_generative_ai.dart';

class GeminiService {
  final model = GenerativeModel(
    model: 'gemini-2.5-flash-image',
    apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY',
  );

  Future<String?> generateDesign(String imageBase64, String style) async {
    final prompt = "Reimagine this room in a $style style...";
    final content = [
      Content.multi([
        TextPart(prompt),
        DataPart('image/png', base64Decode(imageBase64)),
      ])
    ];

    final response = await model.generateContent(content);
    // Find image part in response.candidates
    // Return base64 string
  }
}
```

### 3. UI Structure (Widgets)
React ke components ko aap Flutter Widgets mein map karenge:

| React Component | Flutter Widget |
| :--- | :--- |
| `App.tsx` | `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` |
| `ImageInput.tsx` | `ImagePicker` integration inside a `GestureDetector` |
| `CompareSlider.tsx` | `before_after` package or `Stack` with `ClipRect` |
| `StyleCarousel.tsx` | `ListView.builder` with `scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal` |
| `ChatInterface.tsx` | `ListView` for messages and a `TextField` footer |

### 4. Image Handling
React mein hum `data:image/png;base64,...` use karte hain. Flutter mein:
*   Image display karne ke liye: `Image.memory(base64Decode(yourString))` use karein.
*   Image pick karne ke liye: `image_picker` aapko aik `XFile` dega, jise aap `readAsBytes()` kar ke base64 mein convert kar sakte hain.

### 5. Local Storage
React ke `localStorage` ki jagah Flutter mein aap `shared_preferences` ya `isar` (NoSQL database) use karenge design save karne ke liye.

### Kya aap chahte hain ke main kisi specific widget (jaise Compare Slider) ka Flutter code likh kar dikhaon?

Flutter mein Lumina Space jaisi app banane ke liye aapko **Dart** language aur **Flutter SDK** ki zaroorat hogi. Kyunki main yahan complete `.zip` file nahi de sakta, main aapko woh saari files de raha hon jo aap aik naye Flutter project mein copy-paste kar ke app chala sakte hain.

### Step 1: Naya Flutter Project Banayein
Apne terminal mein yeh command chalayein:
```bash
flutter create lumina_space
cd lumina_space
```

### Step 2: Dependencies Add Karein (`pubspec.yaml`)
Apni `pubspec.yaml` file mein `dependencies` section mein yeh add karein:

```yaml
dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter
  google_generative_ai: ^0.4.0
  image_picker: ^1.1.2
  shared_preferences: ^2.2.3
  before_after: ^2.1.0
  http: ^1.2.1
  path_provider: ^2.1.3
  url_launcher: ^6.2.5
```
Phir terminal mein `flutter pub get` chalayein.

### Step 3: Complete App Code (`lib/main.dart`)
Yeh aik single-file implementation hai jo aapke saare features (Image picking, Style selection, Gemini API, aur Chat) ko handle karegi.

```dart
import 'dart:convert';
import 'dart:io';
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:google_generative_ai/google_generative_ai.dart';
import 'package:image_picker/image_picker.dart';
import 'package:before_after/before_after.dart';
import 'package:shared_preferences/shared_preferences.dart';
import 'package:url_launcher/url_launcher.dart';

// --- CONFIGURATION ---
const String GEMINI_API_KEY = "YOUR_API_KEY_HERE"; // Apna API Key yahan dalein

void main() {
  runApp(const LuminaSpaceApp());
}

class LuminaSpaceApp extends StatelessWidget {
  const LuminaSpaceApp({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return MaterialApp(
      title: 'Lumina Space',
      debugShowCheckedModeBanner: false,
      theme: ThemeData(
        colorScheme: ColorScheme.fromSeed(seedColor: Colors.indigo, brightness: Brightness.light),
        useMaterial3: true,
        fontFamily: 'Inter',
      ),
      home: const HomeScreen(),
    );
  }
}

// --- MODELS ---
enum DesignStyle {
  midCenturyModern('Mid-Century Modern', '🏺'),
  scandinavian('Scandinavian', '❄️'),
  industrial('Industrial', '🏗️'),
  minimalist('Minimalist', '⚪'),
  bohemian('Bohemian', '🌿'),
  japandi('Japandi', '🎍'),
  artDeco('Art Deco', '💎'),
  farmhouse('Farmhouse', '🏠');

  final String label;
  final String icon;
  const DesignStyle(this.label, this.icon);
}

class ChatMessage {
  final String text;
  final bool isUser;
  final List<Map<String, String>>? links;
  ChatMessage({required this.text, required this.isUser, this.links});
}

// --- MAIN SCREEN ---
class HomeScreen extends StatefulWidget {
  const HomeScreen({super.key});

  @override
  State<HomeScreen> createState() => _HomeScreenState();
}

class _HomeScreenState extends State<HomeScreen> {
  File? _originalImage;
  String? _modifiedBase64;
  bool _isLoading = false;
  DesignStyle? _selectedStyle;
  final List<ChatMessage> _chatMessages = [];
  final TextEditingController _chatController = TextEditingController();
  final ImagePicker _picker = ImagePicker();

  // Pick Image from Gallery/Camera
  Future<void> _pickImage(ImageSource source) async {
    final XFile? pickedFile = await _picker.pickImage(source: source);
    if (pickedFile != null) {
      setState(() {
        _originalImage = File(pickedFile.path);
        _modifiedBase64 = null;
        _selectedStyle = null;
      });
    }
  }

  // Generate Image using Gemini
  Future<void> _generateDesign(DesignStyle style) async {
    if (_originalImage == null) return;

    setState(() {
      _isLoading = true;
      _selectedStyle = style;
    });

    try {
      final model = GenerativeModel(model: 'gemini-2.5-flash-image', apiKey: GEMINI_API_KEY);
      final bytes = await _originalImage!.readAsBytes();

      final prompt = "Reimagine this room in a ${style.label} style. Update furniture and decor but keep structure.";
      final content = [
        Content.multi([
          TextPart(prompt),
          DataPart('image/png', bytes),
        ])
      ];

      final response = await model.generateContent(content);

      // Note: Actual image extraction depends on the specific response format of the model
      // This is a simplified logic for the tutorial
      final imagePart = response.candidates.first.content.parts.whereType<InlineDataPart>().firstOrNull;

      if (imagePart != null) {
        setState(() {
          _modifiedBase64 = base64Encode(imagePart.data);
        });
      }
    } catch (e) {
      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(SnackBar(content: Text("Error: $e")));
    } finally {
      setState(() => _isLoading = false);
    }
  }

  // Chat with AI Consultant
  Future<void> _sendChatMessage() async {
    final text = _chatController.text.trim();
    if (text.isEmpty) return;

    setState(() {
      _chatMessages.add(ChatMessage(text: text, isUser: true));
      _chatController.clear();
    });

    try {
      final model = GenerativeModel(model: 'gemini-3-pro-preview', apiKey: GEMINI_API_KEY);
      final response = await model.generateContent([Content.text(text)]);

      setState(() {
        _chatMessages.add(ChatMessage(text: response.text ?? "I'm not sure...", isUser: false));
      });
    } catch (e) {
      print(e);
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      appBar: AppBar(
        title: const Text("Lumina Space", style: TextStyle(fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
        centerTitle: true,
        backgroundColor: Colors.white,
        elevation: 0,
      ),
      body: SingleChildScrollView(
        child: Padding(
          padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16.0),
          child: Column(
            crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
            children: [
              // 1. Image View Area
              _buildImageViewer(),
              const SizedBox(height: 24),

              // 2. Style Carousel
              const Text("Choose Style", style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
              const SizedBox(height: 12),
              _buildStyleCarousel(),
              const SizedBox(height: 32),

              // 3. AI Chat Section
              const Text("AI Design Consultant", style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
              const SizedBox(height: 12),
              _buildChatInterface(),
            ],
          ),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildImageViewer() {
    if (_originalImage == null) {
      return Container(
        height: 250,
        width: double.infinity,
        decoration: BoxDecoration(
          color: Colors.grey[100],
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(24),
          border: Border.all(color: Colors.grey[300]!, width: 2, style: BorderStyle.solid),
        ),
        child: Column(
          mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
          children: [
            Icon(Icons.add_a_photo_outlined, size: 50, color: Colors.indigo[300]),
            const SizedBox(height: 12),
            ElevatedButton(
              onPressed: () => _pickImage(ImageSource.gallery),
              child: const Text("Upload Room Photo"),
            ),
          ],
        ),
      );
    }

    return Container(
      height: 300,
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(24),
        boxShadow: [BoxShadow(color: Colors.black.withOpacity(0.1), blurRadius: 10)],
      ),
      clipBehavior: Clip.antiAlias,
      child: Stack(
        children: [
          if (_modifiedBase64 == null)
            Image.file(_originalImage!, fit: BoxFit.cover, width: double.infinity, height: double.infinity)
          else
            BeforeAfter(
              before: Image.file(_originalImage!, fit: BoxFit.cover),
              after: Image.memory(base64Decode(_modifiedBase64!), fit: BoxFit.cover),
            ),
          if (_isLoading)
            Container(
              color: Colors.black26,
              child: const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator(color: Colors.white)),
            ),
          Positioned(
            top: 10, right: 10,
            child: CircleAvatar(
              backgroundColor: Colors.white,
              child: IconButton(icon: const Icon(Icons.refresh), onPressed: () => setState(() => _originalImage = null)),
            ),
          )
        ],
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildStyleCarousel() {
    return SizedBox(
      height: 120,
      child: ListView.builder(
        scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal,
        itemCount: DesignStyle.values.length,
        itemBuilder: (context, index) {
          final style = DesignStyle.values[index];
          final isSelected = _selectedStyle == style;
          return GestureDetector(
            onTap: () => _generateDesign(style),
            child: Container(
              width: 100,
              margin: const EdgeInsets.only(right: 12),
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
                color: isSelected ? Colors.indigo[50] : Colors.white,
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20),
                border: Border.all(color: isSelected ? Colors.indigo : Colors.grey[200]!),
              ),
              child: Column(
                mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
                children: [
                  Text(style.icon, style: const TextStyle(fontSize: 30)),
                  const SizedBox(height: 8),
                  Text(style.label, textAlign: TextAlign.center, style: const TextStyle(fontSize: 10, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
                ],
              ),
            ),
          );
        },
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildChatInterface() {
    return Container(
      height: 400,
      decoration: BoxDecoration(
        color: Colors.white,
        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(24),
        border: Border.all(color: Colors.grey[200]!),
      ),
      child: Column(
        children: [
          Expanded(
            child: ListView.builder(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.all(12),
              itemCount: _chatMessages.length,
              itemBuilder: (context, index) {
                final msg = _chatMessages[index];
                return Align(
                  alignment: msg.isUser ? Alignment.centerRight : Alignment.centerLeft,
                  child: Container(
                    margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 4),
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.all(12),
                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                      color: msg.isUser ? Colors.indigo : Colors.grey[100],
                      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
                    ),
                    child: Text(msg.text, style: TextStyle(color: msg.isUser ? Colors.white : Colors.black87, fontSize: 13)),
                  ),
                );
              },
            ),
          ),
          Padding(
            padding: const EdgeInsets.all(8.0),
            child: Row(
              children: [
                Expanded(
                  child: TextField(
                    controller: _chatController,
                    decoration: InputDecoration(
                      hintText: "Ask for furniture links...",
                      filled: true,
                      fillColor: Colors.grey[50],
                      border: OutlineInputBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12), borderSide: BorderSide.none),
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
                const SizedBox(width: 8),
                IconButton.filled(onPressed: _sendChatMessage, icon: const Icon(Icons.send)),
              ],
            ),
          )
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

### Is Code ki Khasusiyat:
1.  **Image Comparison**: Ismein `before_after` widget use kiya gaya hai taake aap slider se tabdeeli dekh sakein.
2.  **Gemini Flash & Pro**: Image ke liye Flash aur chat ke liye Pro model integrate kiya gaya hai.
3.  **Material 3 UI**: App bilkul modern Material Design 3 guidelines par bani hai.
4.  **Interactive Styles**: Style choose karte hi AI room ko reimagined karna shuru kar deta hai.

### Setup Tips:
*   **API Key**: `GEMINI_API_KEY` mein apna Google AI Studio wala key zaroor dalein.
*   **Assets**: Aap fonts aur icons customize kar sakte hain, lekin yeh code default system fonts par bhi achha dikhega.
*   **Permissions**: Android/iOS ke liye `AndroidManifest.xml` aur `Info.plist` mein camera aur gallery ki permissions zaroor add karein.

Kya aapko permissions (iOS/Android settings) add karne mein help chahye?

