### Ek aur zaroori cheez: `app.json`
Native app mein permissions manage karne ke liye, apne naye project ke `app.json` file mein yeh settings zaroor add karein:

```json
{
  "expo": {
    "name": "Lumina Space",
    "slug": "lumina-space",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "plugins": [
      [
        "expo-image-picker",
        {
          "photosPermission": "The app needs access to your photos to redesign your room.",
          "cameraPermission": "The app needs access to your camera to snap room photos."
        }
      ]
    ]
  }
}
```

Ab aap `npx expo start` karke apne phone par **Expo Go** app download karein aur QR code scan karein. Aapki app native environment mein chalne lagegi!

